Unity Dev Notes

Maya Shortcut Keys
==================

D Key moves the handle up and down. 

V Key Snaps to vertex

X Key Snapsto grid

Tool options to fine tune Polygons.

Target Welding - Delete faces and go to Mesh tools > Target weld. Drag Edges or vertexs together. (change options to weld to the center)

Mesh combine.

B Key is a soft move

Grow selection select a face hold shift + '.'

Selection

Click one face >> Shift double click on another face to select all faces in edge loop. 


Character modeling 

1. cube 
2. remname
3. position
4. Change center
5. Parenting
6. Freeze Transformations